text: Hortence Vane Mballa Atangana (born 5 January 1992) is a Cameroonian judoka. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women's -78kg. ==References== Category:Olympic judoka of Cameroon Category:1992 births Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:Cameroonian female judoka Category:African Games bronze medalists for Cameroon Category:African Games medalists in judo Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games Category:African Games silver medalists for Cameroon Category:African Games competitors for Cameroon
